title.narrative: Indonesia Forest Law Enforcement Governance and Trade Partnership (FLEGT VPA) Coordination Unit 2014 to 2017

description.narrative: This activity (Indonesia Forest Law Enforcement Governance and Trade Partnership (FLEGT VPA) Coordination Unit 2014 to 2017) is a component of Forest Governance, Markets and Climate reported by FCDO, with a funding type of 'Procurement of Services' and a budget of £1,917,030. This component benefits Indonesia, and works in the following sector(s): Forestry policy and administrative management. , with the following implementing partners: Foreign, Commonwealth and Development Office. The start date is 01-04-2014 and the end date is 31-03-2023.
